                    "text": "3,000 gp",
                    "value": 3000,
                    "currency": "gp"
                },
                "text": "The pendant grants a +2 item bonus to Nature checks (+3 to Command an Animal of the type depicted by the pendant). Once per day, when you use the Broken Tusk pendant's activation, if the animal misses you, the Broken Tusk pendant casts dominate on the animal (DC 30). You can choose whether to use this once-per-day effect after the animal misses you.",
